.SH NAME
dev_pm_genpd_add_notifier \- Add a genpd power on/off notifier for @dev
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" dev_pm_genpd_add_notifier
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "struct notifier_block *nb "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
Device that should be associated with the notifier
.IP "nb" 12
The notifier block to register
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Users may call this function to add a genpd power on/off notifier for an
attached \fIdev\fP. Only one notifier per device is allowed. The notifier is
sent when genpd is powering on/off the PM domain.

It is assumed that the user guarantee that the genpd wouldn't be detached
while this routine is getting called.

Returns 0 on success and negative error values on failures.
